values:
This is interesting:

Wow...lots of arms. that was my first try...I'll try again another time. HEY! Come visit my studio sometime, but you have to call me first..and you have to be special to know my number. Andrew
Here is a photo I took a couple weeks back...

Tina said I should writing interesting posts.

So, I shot another model today.  Chermaine.  She's nice.  It was her first shoot, and she did well.  Hopefully the film shots I took of her, with my lights, will turn out.  That would be nice.

This is not interesting.

I need to work out 7 days a week, since I can because I have nothing much else to do since I'm not teaching now.

I passed the last CSET test...so now there is nothing holding me back from teaching next year.  Just need to double-check with the district about htat...and then, if things work out, then I'll teach.  IF they don't, then I wont teach, I'll just be a bum.

Andrew

So this is my first post. I'm not sure if I'll end up using this site, but we'll see. Thanks Tiffany.
